734
00:50:42,374 --> 00:50:45,377
I don't know you well enough.

735
00:50:45,460 --> 00:50:48,797
I've never been
in a man's apartment alone.

736
00:50:50,632 --> 00:50:53,468
Well, they're all
the same, you know?

737
00:50:58,640 --> 00:51:01,184
I'm not sure I know you well enough.

738
00:51:02,561 --> 00:51:04,604
I don't feel comfortable.

739
00:51:04,813 --> 00:51:07,649
Yo, Adrian,
I ain't so comfortable either.

740
00:51:10,068 --> 00:51:11,611
