permit me to introduce</i>

1424
01:44:25,510 --> 01:44:28,680
<i>the many luminaries of politics,</i>

1425
01:44:28,722 --> 01:44:33,185
<i>show business and the sporting world
who are with us tonight</i>

1426
01:44:33,518 --> 01:44:35,687
<i>but I would like to present</i>

1427
01:44:35,729 --> 01:44:38,815
<i>one of the immortals of pugilism,</i>

1428
01:44:38,857 --> 01:44:42,527
<i>a champion in and out of the ring,</i>

1429
01:44:42,611 --> 01:44:45,364
<i>Philadelphia's own "Smoking Joe,"</i>

1430
01:44:45,447 --> 01:44:48,283
<i>the beloved Mr. Joe Frazier!</i>

1431
01:44:59,044 --> 01:45:00,337
How you doing?

1432
01:45:00,379 --> 01:45:01,838
Don't hurt him, okay?

1433
01:45:01,880 --> 01:45:03,548
I'll try not to.

1434
01:45:03,590 --> 01:45:06,009
<i>What a credit he's been
in his career as a fighter</i>

1435
01:45:06,051 --> 01:45:08,220
<i>Now he's coming over
to talk to the champ.</i>

1436
01:45:08,261 --> 01:45:10,722
- Hey, Joe.
- You been ducking me a long time.

1437
01:45:10,806 --> 01:45:12,474
No, Joe. You're next.

1438
01:45:12,557 --> 01:45:14,768
- You're next.
- You understand?

1439
01:45:15,310 --> 01:45:16,895
They must be friends.

1440
01:45:25,278 --> 01:45:27,114
Joe Frazier!

1441
01:45:27,197 --> 01:45:29,408
<i>- Fight fans, get settled down.
- Go home!</i>

1442
01:45:29,449 --> 01:45:32,619
<i>- Don't stay in the arena!
- It won't be long now.</i>

1443
01:45:34,079 --> 01:45:37,541
<i>Now for the main event.</i>

1444
01:45:41,253 --> 01:45:42,879
<i>On my left</i>

1445
01:45:42,921 --> 01:45:46,091
<i>the challenger, in white trunks,</i>

1446
01:45:46,133 --> 01:45:49,302
<i>weighing 190 pounds.</i>

1447
01:45:49,386 --> 01:45:51,888
<i>Philadelphia's favorite son,</i>

1448
01:45:51,930 --> 01:45:54,808
<i>The Italian Stallion,</i>

1449
01:45:54,891 --> 01:45:56,977
<i>Rocky Balboa.</i>

1450
01:46:03,942 --> 01:46:06,278
<i>And on my right</i>

1451
01:46:06,319 --> 01:46:08,780
<i>wearing red, white and blue,</i>

1452
01:46:08,864 --> 01:46:11,992
<i>weighing 210 pounds,</i>

1453
01:46:12,075 --> 01:46:15,495
<i>undefeated in 46 fights,</i>

1454
01:46:15,787 --> 01:46:18,290
<i>The Master of Disaster,</i>

1455
01:46:18,790 --> 01:46:22,502
<i>the undisputed heavyweight champion
of the world,</i>

1456
01:46:22,586 --> 01:46:24,379
<i>Apollo Creed!</i>

1457
01:46:26,173 --> 01:46:28,717
I want you! You!

1458
01:46:31,428 --> 01:46:34,264
You, chump. I want you!

1459
01:46:34,306 --> 01:46:37,309
You've both fought in
Philadelphia before. You know the rules.

1460
01:46:37,392 --> 01:46:40,562
No low blows,
watch your heads, no butting.

1461
01:46:40,645 --> 01:46:42,397
Shake hands and come out fighting.

1462
01:46:42,481 --> 01:46:44,149
Put your hands up there, chump.

1463
01:46:44,191 --> 01:46:46,318
- Come out fighting.
- Come on!

1464
01:46:48,361 --> 01:46:53,241
<i>Rocky's just going over and
being calm, it looks like from here.</i>

1465
01:46:54,367 --> 01:46:56,286
<i>There goes the big hat.</i>

1466
01:46:59,748 --> 01:47:03,335
<i>I've never seen a fighter
that concerned about his hair.</i>

1467
01:47:11,384 --> 01:47:13,678
<i>There's the bell for round one.</i>

1468
01:47:15,180 --> 01:47:19,309
<i>The fighters come in the center of
the ring, looking at each other.</i>

1469
01:47:19,351 --> 01:47:22,854
<i>Creed, the champion,
zipping in those left-handed jabs.</i>

1470
01:47:22,896 --> 01:47:24,856
<i>Right there. Bang.</i>

1471
01:47:26,483 --> 01:47:29,694
<i>The champ stinging the slower
challenger with jabs at will.</i>

1472
01:47:29,736 --> 01:47:33,740
<i>In fact, it looks like Rocky
is blocking the blows with his face.</i>

1473
01:47:33,824 --> 01:47:38,203
<i>The champion doesn't look the best
he's ever been, but he's moving now.</i>

1474
01:47:38,286 --> 01:47:42,249
<i>The champion's smiling now.
He's toying with him.</i>

1475
01:47:43,041 --> 01:47:46,002
<i>Trying to give the fans
their money's worth.</i>

1476
01:47:47,671 --> 01:47:51,133
<i>He's very clearly outclassed
the challenger right now.</i>

1477
01:47:53,301 --> 01:47:57,222
<i>He's trying to make his
man miss like that.</i>

1478
01:47:58,723 --> 01:48:01,393
<i>The champ is just taunting him.</i>

1479
01:48:04,271 --> 01:48:06,064
<i>Creed dancing around.</i>

1480
01:48:07,524 --> 01:48:09,359
<i>I don't believe this!</i>

1481
01:48:09,401 --> 01:48:11,820
<i>The champ is down!</i>

1482
01:48:17,951 --> 01:48:19,161
<i>Creed is down!</i>

1483
01:48:19,244 --> 01:48:21,204
<i>What a surprise this is!</i>

1484
01:48:22,372 --> 01:48:25,709
<i>This is the first time the champion
has ever been knocked down.</i>

1485
01:48:25,750 --> 01:48:27,961
<i>The referee is giving
him the count.</i>

1486
01:48:28,044 --> 01:48:30,922
Six, seven, eight.

1487
01:48:31,164 --> 01:48:34,250
<i>He appears to be all right.
Glassy-eyed but okay.</i>

1488
01:48:34,259 --> 01:48:37,429
Go to the ribs!
Go to work, Rock!

1489
01:48:37,512 --> 01:48:39,055
Come on!

1490
01:48:40,307 --> 01:48:43,560
<i>Rocky coming back out, and he's
like a bull in a china closet.</i>

1491
01:48:43,602 --> 01:48:46,563
<i>He really wants it.
Apollo, left to the head.</i>

1492
01:48:46,646 --> 01:48:50,358
<i>The champion's coming off the floor</i>

1493
01:48:50,442 --> 01:48:52,527
<i>and he's trying to put him away.</i>

1494
01:48:52,611 --> 01:48:54,112
<i>A left, a right.</i>

1495
01:48:54,196 --> 01:48:57,657
<i>Combinations into the face!
That's the Apollo we know.</i>

1496
01:49:01,786 --> 01:49:05,123
<i>Now the champ is taunting Rocky
to come and get some more.</i>

1497
01:49:05,207 --> 01:49:06,833
<i>A left. Another.</i>

1498
01:49:07,375 --> 01:49:08,877
<i>Another left.</i>

1499
01:49:10,295 --> 01:49:12,130
<i>Rocky's coming back!</i>

1500
01:49:13,590 --> 01:49:16,468
<i>Rocky's got him on the ropes!</i>

1501
01:49:17,302 --> 01:49:18,803
Let's break it.

1502
01:49:20,305 --> 01:49:21,806
You're holding.

1503
01:49:21,890 --> 01:49:23,683
You're posing as a boxer.

1504
01:49:23,767 --> 01:49:26,853
<i>There's no way we expected
this kind of hitting.</i>

1505
01:49:34,444 --> 01:49:38,156
<i>Apollo unloading a left.
He's got him up against the ropes.</i>

1506
01:49:45,914 --> 01:49:50,001
<i>They're leading him to his corner.
Rocky can't find his way.</i>

1507
01:49:50,710 --> 01:49:52,128
I called it!

1508
01:49:52,170 --> 01:49:54,714
- Your nose is broke.
- How's it look?

1509
01:49:54,798 --> 01:49:56,341
It's an improvement.

1510
01:49:56,383 --> 01:49:59,678
Quit shucking and jiving!
Stick and move!

1511
01:49:59,719 --> 01:50:03,223
Go for the ribs.
Don't let that bastard breathe.

1512
01:50:03,306 --> 01:50:04,724
The guy's quick.

1513
01:50:05,850 --> 01:50:08,645
He doesn't know it's a damn show.
He thinks it's a damn fight.

1514
01:50:08,687 --> 01:50:11,398
Finish this bum, and let's go home.

1515
01:50:12,399 --> 01:50:14,818
Stay to the body.
You're doing great!

1516
01:50:14,859 --> 01:50:18,113
<i>Round two. Creed predicted
he'd win it in three.</i>

1517
01:50:18,196 --> 01:50:21,741
<i>Creed got knocked down in the first.
He came back strong.</i>

1518
01:50:22,117 --> 01:50:23,785
<i>He's working hard.</i>

1519
01:50:24,202 --> 01:50:26,955
<i>A sharp left.
Again, a hard right.</i>

1520
01:50:27,038 --> 01:50:29,541
<i>Now coming in.
He's knocked him into the corner again.</i>

1521
01:50:29,582 --> 01:50:32,127
<i>The champion's got him
backed into the corner.</i>

1522
01:50:32,210 --> 01:50:36,131
<i>Pummeling him left and right,
his head bouncing against the ropes.</i>

1523
01:50:37,007 --> 01:50:40,051
<i>Balboa's taking
a tremendous beating here.</i>

1524
01:50:40,135 --> 01:50:43,722
<i>Battering him like a punching bag.
What's keeping him up?</i>

1525
01:50:46,057 --> 01:50:47,559
Can't you fight?

1526
01:50:47,600 --> 01:50:50,895
Stop clowning around
and give the people something!

1527
01:50:51,563 --> 01:50:53,898
<i>- Come on!
- He says he wants more!</i>

1528
01:50:53,940 --> 01:50:56,735
<i>He wants more. You folks
watching television around the world</i>

1529
01:50:56,818 --> 01:50:58,903
<i>you're watching a battle.</i>

1530
01:51:03,658 --> 01:51:06,953
<i>Balboa trying to fight back.
Oh, he tagged the champ!</i>

1531
01:51:07,037 --> 01:51:10,582
<i>The champion is trying to get out
of there, but he can't do it.</i>

1532
01:51:10,623 --> 01:51:14,544
<i>He is being barraged with lefts
and rights to the head and body.</i>

1533
01:51:14,586 --> 01:51:17,922
<i>Balboa is tagging the champion
right on the kisser!</i>

1534
01:51:19,090 --> 01:51:22,302
<i>The referee steps in.
They're ready to keep going.</i>

1535
01:51:22,719 --> 01:51:24,554
Back to your corners!

1536
01:51:25,180 --> 01:51:27,098
Come on, Creed!

1537
01:51:27,849 --> 01:51:30,101
<i>This is gonna be a tough one.</i>

1538
01:52:24,697 --> 01:52:27,075
<i>- Back with a left!
- He got tagged!</i>

1539
01:52:28,660 --> 01:52:31,246
<i>The referee's wiping
off the gloves.</i>

1540
01:52:36,459 --> 01:52:38,795
<i>Hard left and right
combination!</i>

1541
01:52:38,837 --> 01:52:41,798
<i>- What is keeping him up, Bill?
- I don't know.</i>

1542
01:52:43,758 --> 01:52:47,011
<i>He can't even get his gloves up
to protect himself.</i>

1543
01:52:54,477 --> 01:52:56,521
Down! Stay down!

1544
01:52:56,604 --> 01:52:58,940
<i>Apollo has his arms in the air!</i>

1545
01:53:09,993 --> 01:53:11,119
Five.

1546
01:53:12,370 --> 01:53:13,496
Six.

1547
01:53:14,038 --> 01:53:15,248
Seven.

1548
01:53:15,331 --> 01:53:16,541
Eight.

1549
01:53:16,916 --> 01:53:18,042
Nine.

1550
01:53:24,883 --> 01:53:26,176
Come on!

1551
01:53:27,427 --> 01:53:29,429
<i>Apollo can't believe it.</i>

1552
01:53:46,237 --> 01:53:49,407
<i>The champion got a left
to his right ribs.</i>

1553
01:53:49,782 --> 01:53:52,035
<i>This has been a tremendous...</i>

1554
01:53:57,790 --> 01:53:58,958
Okay, champ?

1555
01:53:59,042 --> 01:54:00,376
Yeah, I'm okay.

1556
01:54:00,418 --> 01:54:03,087
I may have broke my ribs.

1557
01:54:03,129 --> 01:54:05,590
I can't see nothing.
Gotta open my eye.

1558
01:54:05,673 --> 01:54:07,592
- Cut me.
- Don't wanna do it.

1559
01:54:07,675 --> 01:54:10,220
- Go ahead. Cut me.
- Okay.

1560
01:54:10,261 --> 01:54:11,804
Try it. Cut it.

1561
01:54:12,263 --> 01:54:14,140
Creed! Creed!

1562
01:54:16,100 --> 01:54:17,352
Oh, God.

1563
01:54:17,435 --> 01:54:20,230
You're bleeding inside.
I'm gonna stop the fight.

1564
01:54:20,271 --> 01:54:23,608
You ain't stopping
nothing, man.

1565
01:54:23,775 --> 01:54:26,277
You stop this fight,
I'll kill you!

1566
01:54:27,612 --> 01:54:29,781
- I'm going.
- If you wanna go.

1567
01:54:31,032 --> 01:54:33,368
You gotta give it all!

1568
01:54:33,451 --> 01:54:35,411
You gotta get him!

1569
01:54:40,875 --> 01:54:42,794
<i>The 15th and final round.</i>

1570
01:54:42,877 --> 01:54:45,922
Rocky! Rocky! Rocky!

1571
01:54:51,761 --> 01:54:54,389
<i>They look like they've been in a war.</i>

1572
01:55:01,980 --> 01:55:05,400
<i>A hard right.
The champion really tagged him.</i>

1573
01:55:05,483 --> 01:55:09,445
<i>Apollo clearly protecting
his right side, his ribs.</i>

1574
01:55:12,824 --> 01:55:14,659
<i>Body punches!</i>

1575
01:55:14,701 --> 01:55:18,162
<i>Hard lefts and rights. Look at the
blood coming out of his mouth!</i>

1576
01:55:18,204 --> 01:55:20,331
<i>He's spitting up blood now.</i>

1577
01:55:23,835 --> 01:55:26,337
<i>A tremendous right hand by Rocky.</i>

1578
01:55:26,379 --> 01:55:27,797
Go for it, Rock!

1579
01:55:27,839 --> 01:55:30,842
<i>- Listen to this crowd!
- Right to the ribs.</i>

1580
01:55:30,925 --> 01:55:33,261
<i>Another to the ribs.
That left hand again.</i>

1581
01:55:33,344 --> 01:55:36,598
<i>Right to the jaw!
He's got him up against the ropes!</i>

1582
01:55:36,681 --> 01:55:38,766
<i>Apollo the champ...</i>

1583
01:55:42,228 --> 01:55:44,981
Ain't gonna be no rematch.

1584
01:55:45,607 --> 01:55:47,150
Don't want one.

1585
01:55:57,660 --> 01:56:00,622
Rocky, you went the distance,
15 rounds. How do you feel?

1586
01:56:00,705 --> 01:56:03,207
- All right.
- What were you thinking about...

1587
01:56:03,249 --> 01:56:05,918
- Adrian!
- ...coming out for the 15th round?

1588
01:56:06,002 --> 01:56:07,253
Adrian!

1589
01:56:09,255 --> 01:56:10,381
Rocky!

1590
01:56:14,719 --> 01:56:16,596
<i>- Tonight...</i>
- Rocky!

1591
01:56:16,679 --> 01:56:19,724
<i>...we have had the
privilege of witnessing</i>

1592
01:56:19,766 --> 01:56:23,394
<i>the greatest exhibition
of boxing stamina</i>

1593
01:56:23,478 --> 01:56:25,605
<i>in the history of the ring.</i>

1594
01:56:25,688 --> 01:56:27,231
Adrian!

1595
01:56:28,066 --> 01:56:29,233
Rocky!

1596
01:56:30,109 --> 01:56:32,236
<i>Ladies and gentlemen,</i>

1597
01:56:32,278 --> 01:56:35,114
<i>we have a split decision.</i>

1598
01:56:36,324 --> 01:56:37,742
<i>Judge Walker</i>

1599
01:56:41,245 --> 01:56:42,580
<i>for Creed!</i>

1600
01:56:45,291 --> 01:56:46,459
Adrian!

1601
01:56:46,584 --> 01:56:50,088
- Your fans want a rematch.
- Ain't gonna be no rematch!

1602
01:56:51,881 --> 01:56:53,633
- Adrian!
- You heard him...

1603
01:56:53,716 --> 01:56:56,844
- You can't go in there!
- That's my friend. Let go!

1604
01:56:56,928 --> 01:56:59,430
- You're wrecking the jacket!
- Rocky!

1605
01:56:59,472 --> 01:57:02,100
- Paulie.
- Adrian!

1606
01:57:06,270 --> 01:57:07,522
I love you!

1607
01:57:07,605 --> 01:57:08,981
I love you!

1608
01:57:12,610 --> 01:57:15,154
- I love you!
- I love you!

1609
01:57:15,238 --> 01:57:16,823
I love you!